subject: Creating unit tests for non returning methods
msgSnippet: Hello All, I have used JUnit before, however I have been unable to figure out how to test methods that don t have a return value. How do you test those types
messageBody:
Hello All,

I have used JUnit before, however I have been unable to figure out how
to test methods that don't have a return value. How do you test those
types of methods? Do all methods have to return a value to be able to
develop a test for it?

-Paul
